data.description: Attention first time home buyers or investors. This super cute 3 Bedroom 2 bath home located in Bellemead is perfect for a first-time home or if you're looking to build your rental portfolio. The kitchen is open, the back yard is spacious, and the HVAC less than 3 years old. With some minor cosmetic work, this home will be move in ready. Grab your favorite real estate professional and schedule a viewing. This home qualifies for grant funds up to $5,000.
